IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Daniel Dean BLIEK and Lori Lee Bliek Upon the Petition of Daniel Dean Bliek, Petitioner-Appellant, And Concerning Lori Lee Bliek, Respondent-Appellee. No. 17-2029 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed December 19, 2018

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

Daniel Bliek appeals from the district court's order granting Lori Bliek's petition to modify the spousal support provision of the parties' 2013 dissolution decree. REVERSED.

REVERSED.
